Site name: Conjugaison Puzzle

Site description:
Conjugaison Puzzle is an interactive educational game designed to demystify French verb conjugation.
It visualizes verb construction by decomposing forms into logical components
(Stems or Auxiliaries + Endings or Participles),
covering 14 core French tenses across simple and compound forms.

Primary purpose:
To provide a visual, logic-based interface for practicing French grammar rules
and verb conjugation patterns through gamified interaction.

Content includes:
- Logic-based decomposition of French verb conjugation
- Simple tenses: Base + Ending
- Compound tenses: Auxiliary + Past Participle
- Full coverage of Indicative, Subjunctive, and Conditional moods
- Interactive drag-and-drop conjugation puzzles
- Multi-language grammar explanations

